      "raw_text": "Contractor Peter Costello has been\ndumping rock and earth on the North\nern Pacific right-of-way between\nWashington street and Bernard street,\nso the Northern Pacific people allege.\nThey stated that Costello has no au-\nthority from them to do SO. Further\nmore 1t is said Costello will continue\nto dump on their land until restrain\ned by the courts. Accordingly. as\nthe contractor is insolvent and I'M\nable to respond to damages, a tenn\nporary restraining order is wanted\nuntil notice be served and an injunc-\ntion made perpetual. The order was\nmade by Judge KEENAN, today."
    }
